  "reference_number": "RUS1670",
  "remarks": "\nAndrey BUROV is an involved person within the meaning of the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 because he is the Chairperson of the Rostov Regional Election Commission. The Rostov Regional Election Commission assisted the voting in the illegitimate Russian referendums held in temporarily-occupied areas of Ukraine. Through this role, BUROV is or has engaged in policies or actions which destabilise Ukraine and undermine or threaten the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine. \n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
